      <title>洛杉矶市政公用事业公司债券发售因火灾而陷入困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/los-angeles-muni-utility-s-bond-sale-is-in-limbo-amid-fires</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，洛杉矶水电局发行的债券原定于本周定价，但由于南加州发生山火，该局于周一将债券定价转为“每日定价”。这位知情人士在讨论该交易时不愿透露姓名。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/los-angeles-muni-utility-s-bond-sale-is-in-limbo-amid-fires</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 18:16:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
