      <title>西班牙拟对非欧盟公民购房征收 100% 税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/spain-to-try-to-limit-real-estate-purchases-by-non-eu-residents</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙要求非欧盟居民在该国购房时缴纳高达 100% 的税，此举可能会影响来自英国和拉丁美洲的买家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/spain-to-try-to-limit-real-estate-purchases-by-non-eu-residents</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 11:50:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
